OL,3,C'We met as grieving dads, now we're
OL,4,Cfriends for life'
OL,6,F"Three Dads Walking, 300 Miles of
OL,7,FHope" tells the story of Mike Palmer
OL,8,Ffrom Sale, Andy Airey from Cumbria and
OL,9,FTim Owen from Norfolk's , as they
OL,10,Fattempted to raise awareness of the
OL,11,Fbiggest killer of under 35s.
OL,13,FIn memory of their daughters ` Sophie,
OL,14,FBeth and Emily ` their walk took them
OL,15,Facross Britain from each of their
OL,16,Fhomes in Cumbria, Greater Manchester
OL,17,Fand Norfolk, as putting one foot in
OL,18,Ffront of the other, they fought for
OL,19,Ftheir message to be heard.
