OL,6,FTheir book, which is told in three
OL,7,Fdistinct parts by each dad, has been
OL,8,Fput together from their personal
OL,9,Fdiaries of the walk, and they say it
OL,10,Fis "about the power of speaking out,
OL,11,Fof friendship, and hope (and
OL,12,Fblisters)."
