OL,3,C'We met as grieving dads, now we're
OL,4,Cfriends for life'
OL,6,FThe dads released a joint statement
OL,7,Fahead of the book being published:
OL,8,F"The suicide of our daughters sent our
OL,9,Flives on completely unexpected
OL,10,Ftrajectories; however, as we have
OL,11,Fwalked we have realised that talking
OL,12,Fabout our girls and our experiences
OL,13,Fhas helped many other families to
OL,14,Favoid suffering the same fate as us.
OL,16,F"Talking about suicide prevention
OL,17,Fsaves lives and in publishing our
OL,18,Fstory we want to continue to spread
OL,19,Four message of hope.
