OL,3,C'We met as grieving dads, now we're
OL,4,Cfriends for life'
OL,6,F"We were (and are) three ordinary dads
OL,7,Fwho found ourselves in a desperate
OL,8,Fplace we never expected to be,
OL,9,Fengulfed by pain and suffering beyond
OL,10,Fimagining.
OL,12,F"We wanted to do something and this is
OL,13,Fwhat it became ... what we became."
