OL,3,C'We met as grieving dads, now we're
OL,4,Cfriends for life'
OL,6,FTim Owen, from Norfolk, lost his 19-
OL,7,Fyear-old daughter Emily in 2020
OL,9,FAndy Airey from Morland in Cumbria,
OL,10,Flost his 29-year-old daughter Sophie
OL,11,Fin 2018.
OL,13,FA year after their first walk in 2021,
OL,14,Fthey doubled that distance, walking
OL,15,Fbetween the parliaments of all four
OL,16,Fnations from Northern Ireland through
OL,17,FScotland, Wales and England as part of
OL,18,Ftheir campaign to make suicide
OL,19,Fprevention a compulsory part of the
OL,20,Fschool curriculum.
